welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Bryn Mawr-Skyway, a charming city known for its rich history and beautiful natural surroundings. We invite you to explore and embrace all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves commercial flights and houses various amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Jet Terminal
terminals.description: The private jet terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and corporate aircrafts, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is used for cargo and general aviation flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport houses most of the airport's facilities, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and a variety of shops and restaurants.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport primarily serves Alaska Airlines, with a few other airlines also operating out of this terminal.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for international flights, with a few domestic flights also operating out of this terminal.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to 45 minutes per day. Additional time can be purchased for a fee.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the hub for all flights and passenger services.

wifi.note: Passengers can access complimentary wifi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport provides all necessary services for travelers, including check-in, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is exclusively for military personnel and their families, providing easy access to military flights and services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all travelers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The north terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
